description: The culminating event for our coding bootcamp. One last attempt at a fullstack application that will land me a job!
In a most likely futile attempt to outsmart the Beast, we will combine the power of multiple vaccuums to suck up the Babe Ruth ball.
One of the greatest feats accomplished by man. The most amazing thing the sandlot has ever seen.
Using Smalls' erector sets, we will send in a motorized cart with a built-in catapult to launch the Babe Ruth ball over the fence.
Yeah-Yeah will hang from an intricate pulley system to be lowered over the Babe Ruth ball, and hopefully return it to the sandlot.
